My awesome best friend and brother, Geoffrey Ong @jetblackace has passed away. 
We have gone through a lot as kids in high school to as older men in their late 40’s.
Going to all sorts of comic book conventions from the Shrine to San Diego Comic Con. 
Creating our own projects like Backspace.
Have so much great memories with the fellas. 
He was part of my family…we all love him! 
It’s hard to accept this. 
I will need time to process this.

Geoff is pictured with my sisters Ingrid and Walemi…with my nephew Lucas.

Missing you, brother!

Set up a small memorial at home for my beloved brother Geoff @jetblackace 

Wishing you all a peaceful rest of the week.

#family #brotherhood #friendsforever
